snippet.title: Jingle Bells - Kids Christmas Songs

localized.description:
Jingle bells, jingle bells, jingle all the way! Looking for some kids Christmas music? It's the classic Christmas song, performed by Bounce Patrol! 

Links to watch more Bounce Patrol videos:

Learn Colors: http://youtu.be/9Dczg71L_vk
Old MacDonald Had a Farm: http://youtu.be/EGymN-Lc87M

Find Bounce Patrol on:
iTunes: http://itunes.apple.com/us/artist/bounce-patrol/id603391356
Facebook: http://www.facebook.com/BouncePatrol
Web: http://www.bouncepatrol.com

Thanks for watching! Happy Christmas from Bounce Patrol!
